{"tid":1378970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非都可以遊擊隊!!","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:41:53.000Z","uid":21108,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"960cfc47553255f8fe7c3b72777d85b8cb8c8d3e","tid":1378970,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"今日遮打集會大隊行左銅鑼灣<br />\n當時警力集中係西環上環<br />\n咁我地一班本來企左係狗總個路口位<br />\n一直諗緊圍唔圍<br />\n但人數不足<br />\n我地就開始討論做d咩<br />\n勇武未開波<br />\n大隊仲去緊銅鑼灣<br />\n咁我地決定遊走灣仔既政府部門<br />\n人數應該有100左右<br />\n由稅務大樓&gt;會展&gt;政府合署<br />\n我地每個地方都係停留10至15分鐘<br />\n10至15分鐘可以做d咩?<br />\n可以係牆上寫字 可以雞蛋<br />\n總之我地目標有兩個<br />\n每個地點唔會停留太耐<br />\n只會搞政府機關<br />\n(其實會展都係入去嗌口號 正門入 金紫荊廣場出)<br />\n下次再出黎<br />\n希望真係做到遍地開花<br />\n大家有咩提議可以再講<br />\n香港人係不停進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb2ba2c6422c27067e8186c3368a1a9dfd1ca37","tid":1378970,"uid":263161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4a2296fc97f646bd9e6acd26c48165a48c9fbf2","tid":1378970,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"推 下次和理非主動打亂警犬部署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f177a8cf2dcf6ba4a43fc83720a9c0ebac0bf1","tid":1378970,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d212a668033f3daf011cbec0f5d5f98050467caf","tid":1378970,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"要再進化喇"},{"pid":"69c30b29e5eaa5ecd733d09b252239f841dcf020","tid":1378970,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"唔單止前線進化<br />\n和理非都進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass